#

Classic Beet Borshch

75 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupVegetarianComfort Food

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup, packed with flavors and nutrients, perfect for a wholesome meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrot: 1 large, grated
  • potato: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • sour cream: for serving
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • bay leaf: 1
